    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "",
      "subsections": {
        "Rejection": {
          "text": "Patients monitored with surveillance biopsies regularly\nSpectrum of presentations, anywhere asymptomatic to in extremis\nFeatures include\ndysrhythmias\n, decreased exercise tolerance, and\ninfection\nmay be clues",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Infection": {
          "text": "Increased risk of opportunistic/severe\ninfections\nFever\nand other classic features may be absent due to immunosuppression",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Signs/Symptoms_of_Congestive_Heart_Failure": {
          "text": "Due to various etiologies\nMI\nmay present only with CHF symptoms",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Medication_Adverse_Effects": {
          "text": "Prednisone\nHyperglycemia\n, psychiatric symptoms, poor wound healing, edema,\nhypertension\nTacrolimus\n,\ncyclosporine\nNeurotoxicity,\ntremor\n,\nhyperkalemia\n,\nnephrotoxicity\n,\nhypertension\n,\nhyperglycemia\n,\ngout\nMycophenolate\nCytopenias,\nGI distress\nAzathioprine\nCytopenias,\npancreatitis\n,\nhepatitis",
          "tables": []
        },
